- [ ] support explicit handoff cues\n- [ ] keep related threads linked as part of one larger work plan\n\n## Exit Criteria\n\n- multiple Codex threads can be used as a coordinated work set\n- coordination semantics are explicit, not implicit\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
